---
title: One-Pan Shawarma-Spiced Chicken & Rice with Golden Raisins, Carrots & Cilantro Yogurt Sauce
description: Tonight’s spiced chicken has all the typical Middle Eastern-inspired flavors of shawarma, but it’s cooked in one pan. You’ll add carrots, garlic, rice, and raisins to your chicken, then mix it all together with a squeeze of fresh lemon, a drizzle of cilantro crema, and a garnish of almonds. It all adds up to a dinner that’s easy to clean up and even easier to gobble down.
